Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.83,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enjoying the view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.83,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆因此境風景獨好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:24.33,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pike or shield?  負けたくはない　でも傷つけたくもない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:24.33,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矛 or 盾？ 不想認輸 可是又不願受傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:27.32,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手に取って　確かめてた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:27.32,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先挑一樣在手中仔細掂量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.52,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと戻れないんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.52,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是發現再要反悔為時已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:34.97,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:34.97,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選的是哪邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:37.75,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  思い出は枷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:37.75,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  思念是枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:40.27,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  後付けのlove
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:40.27,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  追悔莫及的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:43.08,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  優しさは仇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:43.08,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  溫柔是弱點
